snippet.title: Lost Eidolons: Veil of the Witch Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
A gameplay trailer for Lost Eidolons: Veil of the Witch revealed that the tactical fantasy RPG is launching into early access in November 2024. But if you can't wait that long, there's a demo available on Steam.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#losteidolons #FutureGamesShow #FGS #futuregamesshow2024 #gamescom
